---
title: Sweet & Spicy Pork Chop Lo Mein with Cabbage & Scallions
description: Big bowls of saucy noodles are always a hit on our table. You'll toss tender lo mein noodles with thinly sliced pork chops, cabbage, and peanuts in a soy-chili sauce boosted with extra heat from Sriracha and garnished with scallion greens and peanuts. Best of all, this delicious dish only takes a quick 20 minutes to make!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67bc379687e74f1041b22471-dddc19cf.jpeg
